\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Gell.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.1.32</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n98127.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">=</abbr> Lat. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">delator</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁ πικρὸς ς. Ἰσίδωρος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0018.tlg001:2:597\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.597</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OGI\">OGI</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">669.41</biblScope> </bibl> (Egypt, <date TEIform=\"date\">i A.D.</date>), <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Cod.Just.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.4.34.17</biblScope></bibl>, al. (From <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σῦκον φαίνειν</foreign>, orig. used of denouncers of the attempted export of figs from Athens, acc. to <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1450.tlg001:35\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ister\">Ister</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">35</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg007:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sol.\">Sol.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg007:2:523b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.523b</biblScope> </bibl>; orig. of citizens entrusted with the collection of figs as part of the public revenues of Athens and the denouncing of tax-evaders, acc. to <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1598.tlg001:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\